{"tid":316584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我係動物傳心師，貼圖比我來辯","createTime":"2017-07-10T23:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T00:56:15.000Z","uid":4213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26b42270d446d39cb15c7860a3c70055d9b10d5c","tid":316584,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T23:42:39.000Z","msg":"作為一個專業嘅動物傳心師<br />\n我認為我有需要承擔一切坊間對我地傳心師嘅質疑<br />\n所以係呢個Post 只要你敢貼圖<br />\n我就敢同佢傳心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出招吧！"},{"pid":"32950d41fbcb3038e55f172ed8a51ba862de977e","tid":316584,"uid":84998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T23:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.likecap.com/share/702.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.likecap.com%2Fshare%2F702.jpg&h=e46abd6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"499f5a64dbdc94dc77ece6b1e950be129c357597","tid":316584,"uid":953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T23:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.likecap.com/share/702.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.likecap.com%2Fshare%2F702.jpg&h=e46abd6f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢隻駛閪傳心咩 係人都知隻奸狗諗乜"},{"pid":"e8e5b58c50ed13d886f83d076e846d90bd923fcc","tid":316584,"uid":47674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T23:56:31.000Z","msg":"呢條金魚想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.sudden.nextmedia.com/images/next-photos/SuddenWeekly/965/640pixfolder/A965_045_45a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.sudden.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fnext-photos%2FSuddenWeekly%2F965%2F640pixfolder%2FA965_045_45a.jpg&h=9d78e3c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03bbf2af43036e5bdd89876426bf7ec7eebdfb05","tid":316584,"uid":4285